name: Symfony2colors
body:
### Symfony2 colors for you
Because we care about style and comfort for the developer here you have symfony2 colors for your phpstorm ide.

### Authors and Contributors
Luis Cordova (@cordoval), and Mark Badolato (@mbadolato).

### Support or Contact
Enjoy!
